Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:08.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,没事吧  听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.11,0:00:13.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,一名身份不明三十五岁左右的男子被卡车撞倒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:17.49,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,现已失去意识  并且大量出血
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:13.28,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:14.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那已经没救了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:19.62,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,另外卡车司机安全无事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:22.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,说起来  我被卡车…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:31.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,同样被撞到的两名高中生  目前下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:32.42,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,正在进行搜寻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:34.47,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,请求紧急支援  Over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.80,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那三个人得救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:40.47,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,很重啊  小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:45.85,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是啊  毕竟连饭都是敲地板让人送过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:47.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,连续宅在家二十年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你知道这里是哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.16,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,真吵  不用那么大声我也听得见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:06.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:08.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,血压过低
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:09.04,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,准备输血
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:13.34,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,听得到吗  知道自己的名字吗  能说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:16.01,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我要死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:19.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不过也好  反正我的人生也已经没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:25.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不过至少想要童贞毕业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:40.03,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好耀眼  我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.29,0:01:45.00,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,喂喂  这家伙是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:48.62,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:50.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这么轻易就把我这超100公斤重的汉子抱起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:54.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,什么人啊  不要啊  好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:57.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,啥啊  真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:01.64,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  脸那么红
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.18,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,奶子好大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,说的哪国语言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,话说这是哪  不是医院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:16.86,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这家伙在干什么啊  我可是重伤员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:20.32,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不过这个人真漂亮啊  欧美人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那么没防备的话  我就要摸胸了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:44.76,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,看来是我转生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.64,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,没想到这种做梦一般的事竟然会变成现实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:53.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,保罗和塞妮丝  年龄大概二十岁出头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:57.07,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,从34岁的我看来  说是年轻人也不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.49,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,年纪轻轻就造孩子  真让人嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:04.49,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不过能免费吸美女的奶子真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:08.62,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,虽然因为对方是母亲  完全兴奋不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,鲁迪  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:15.71,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,鲁迪乌斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.97,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我的名字大概是叫鲁迪乌斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:22.93,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,过了半年  也能理解一点语言了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:27.27,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,因为年龄还很小  记性异常地好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,女仆莉莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.24,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,拥有很棒的胸器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:45.87,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,喂  鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.75,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不可以一个人到处乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.00,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这不是拿来戴的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:54.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  莉莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:04:00.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,塞妮丝大人  恕我直言  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.51,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,鲁迪乌斯大人是不是被什么脏东西附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.76,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不  什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:09.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,什么啊  含糊不清的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:12.89,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,小孩子嘛  把内裤套在头上也很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,真是美丽的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.66,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,总感觉我看过这里的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.12,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,果然是在欧洲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:34.12,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,然而这里也太偏远了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}大概这样就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.12,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.75,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那边就拜托你了  莉莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:36.67,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.50,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,电和煤气都没有  这是什么时代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,既然都转生了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我还是想玩玩电脑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:46.47,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.68,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这是在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:53.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.06,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:04:59.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:04:59.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.03,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:09.16,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,头被撞到的时候  不要乱动它比较好哦  这位夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.24,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,居然这都不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:13.58,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,乖  乖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:19.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,以防万一  给你施加个让痛痛飞走的咒语吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,神圣之力如芳醇之食粮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.43,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,喂喂  开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这就是这个国家的「痛痛快飞走」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:37.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}赐予失去力量之人再次站起来的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.98,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,继父亲之后母亲也是中二病吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是战士和僧侣结婚了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.28,Mushoku-Pronunciation,,0,0,0,,Healing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.28,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.62,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎么样  不痛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:02.21,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,别看妈妈我这样  以前可是冒险者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了  我听见好大一声响
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:07.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  鲁迪摔下来撞到头了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,冷静点啊  小孩子就是会经常跌倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:13.06,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}而且就算受伤  你来治好他不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,莫非这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:17.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,可是要是受了重伤我治不好怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:17.98,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.02,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不  已经可以断定了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.02,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这里不是地球  而是别的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.57,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,剑与魔法的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:41.50,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,腰腿也变得结实了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,话说回来  魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:45.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:50.64,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这不是连猴子听到都会为之兴奋的单词吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:53.14,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,真想快点自己试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.89,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,虽说如此  现在的我能做到的事情并不多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:23.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:27.21,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,家里只有五本书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:30.17,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是这个世界的书很昂贵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.39,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,还是因为保罗他们不怎么读书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:36.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,对有上千本书的我来说真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.77,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,虽然全都是轻小说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:40.98,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,读不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,首先还是要搞懂这边的文字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,又过了一年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:52.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,虽然只有五本  有时候保罗也会读给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:54.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我在一定程度上能读懂文字了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:08:00.87,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是  那个老爸很是质疑幼儿能否理解书里的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.21,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,即便如此  我对这本书很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:05.54,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔法课本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.34,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,有些内容仿佛前世也在哪里看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:13.51,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,例如  魔法有咏唱和魔法阵两种发动方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:16.93,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但现在的主流是咏唱  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:19.01,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好像有各种各样的设定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.27,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,而且  让我在意的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:25.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,书上写着  每个人魔力的总量在生下来时就基本固定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:26.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.69,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,感觉自己的遗传因子会没什么作用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:32.82,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不过总而言之先试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:43.21,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,给予你所求之处以水之加护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:47.33,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,清凉细流在此显现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.59,Mushoku-Pronunciation,,0,0,0,,Ｗater Ball
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,水球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎么不飞出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,和格斗游戏的连击练习一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:24.71,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,集中精神  不断在脑海中想象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.04,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,然后试着实际操作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:49.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我还没进行咏唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:51.07,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:57.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,咦  我的MP就这么点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,鲁迪真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.91,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,困了的话要好好上了厕所再到床上睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,都这个年纪还被误会尿床了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.50,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,可恶  可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,经过一段时间的尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:28.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我搞懂很多事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那本书居然骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.98,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔力的总量会随着使用而增加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:36.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不用咏唱也可以使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:39.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是把要写的东西都列举出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是这么轻易就能做到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.37,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,咏唱还有什么意义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:52.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,莫非咏唱是使魔法自动化的原理条件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不用次次都集中精神去感受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,只要出声就能完成一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是这样的话  好处就很大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.14,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,首先第一点  方便传授
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.39,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,咏唱的话就能一次成功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:07.14,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,也许是在传授过程中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:11.31,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,逐渐变成「咏唱是必不可缺的」这种说法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:13.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,第二点  方便使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,攻击魔法是在战斗中使用的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:19.78,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,比起闭上眼睛使劲地集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.78,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,快速咏唱才会更迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.91,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,鲁迪  差不多该睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.58,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:31.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,还没行呢  好戏现在才开始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:33.71,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}亲爱的~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:36.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,为什么魔力总量会增加还是个谜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,也许是进行锻炼的结果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:43.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就算经过努力锻炼  魔力总量也会有上限
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:46.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不  现在下结论还为时尚早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:49.89,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,没错  比如说可能会随着成长而增加之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:54.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,幼儿期使用魔力的话  上限会飞跃性地增加之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:00.28,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,保不齐是唯独我才有的特殊体质呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:02.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,兴奋起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:04.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不行  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:05.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:07.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,如果刚刚的假设没错的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.04,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,要做的事情就只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:10.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在成长期结束之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.33,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,尽最大可能地去锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:14.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.67,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是  这个怎么才能射出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:35.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:49.16,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,做到了  做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.70,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,终于搞清楚吟唱的原理了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.04,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这个魔法是按照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:57.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,「生成-设定大小-设定弹速-发射」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这个流程来完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,应该是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:05.18,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,之前是因为我没有设定弹速才没有射出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.43,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,感觉魔力总量也增加得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:14.77,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,试试中级魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:19.90,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,优柔的水精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:25.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,流淌大地之上溪流之王女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:29.70,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,以汝蕴藏之强力  冲溃世间万物吧
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.54,Mushoku-Pronunciation,,0,0,0,,Splash Flow
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.54,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,激流冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:55.43,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:01.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.78,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,鲁迪  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是魔物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.28,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但这附近不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:18.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,鲁迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.34,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,难道你开口念了这本书上面的内容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:22.29,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:23.55,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这是什么眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,难道说会魔法的小孩很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.80,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,会被送去接受异端审问之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不要  不要火刑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:35.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  你听见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我们家的孩子果然是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.11,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但这可是中级的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,现在就雇个魔法教师过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是在那之前  我还没教过他识字…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:50.24,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,将来肯定是个很厉害的魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:52.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.87,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我们不是约定过是男孩就培养成剑士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是这个年纪就会使用中级魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,约定就是约定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:03.29,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,什么约定  亲爱的总是不遵守约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我的事和这是两码事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,上午学魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,下午练剑不挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  在孩子面前吵架不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:15.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:20.31,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,于是乎我们家就雇佣了一个家庭教师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,虽然一直在家里耍剑  看起来很闲的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:26.69,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,保罗姑且还算是名骑士  负责管理这个村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:27.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,托这个福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.82,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,因此为我这个小孩找个老师并不困难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:34.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但怎么说这也是国家边境上的偏远乡村
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:38.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,虽然担心过会不会有人应聘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.75,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,结果很快就找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:43.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,根据父母的推测
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:46.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,来的人估计是已经隐退的冒险者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:46.50,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:49.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,作为魔法师研究多年魔法的中年人或者老人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.17,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:53.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,长满白须的  一看就知道是魔法师的那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.14,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,之前是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:56.97,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是洛琪希·米格路迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:58.64,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:02.85,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,什么鬼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:03.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,别说胡子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,来了个好像连那里的毛都没长齐的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:07.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,年纪差不多是个初中生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:08.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,萝莉的身形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:08.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,藐视的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:09.78,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,冷淡的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:11.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,集齐三个属性  简直完美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:12.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,请务必嫁给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你就是那个来当家庭教师的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这还真是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:18.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好小只呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:21.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不想被你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.75,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,自卑感吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我不是在说胸部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:29.42,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以我要教的学生在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.38,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,啊  就是这个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,偶尔会有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不过是稍微长大了点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.31,0:16:41.02,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就以为孩子有魔法天份的笨蛋父母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,听到了  洛琪希小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}又扑了个空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.35,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:45.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:50.78,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但我并不认为这个小孩能理解魔法的理论
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:54.82,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,没问题  我家鲁迪很优秀的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:57.87,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我会尽我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在外面教吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.37,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这不是肯定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:14.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔法大致可以分成三类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.93,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,攻击魔法  治愈魔法  召唤魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:24.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,分别有初级  中级  上级  圣级  王级  帝级  神级
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,一共这七个等级
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:30.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,然后使用魔法就需要魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:32.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以要么使用体内的魔力或…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.24,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.45,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:42.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,行吧  总之我现在示范一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你试着模仿一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.66,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,需要咏唱的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.42,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,给予你所求之处以水之加护
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.85,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,清凉细流在此显现
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.18,Mushoku-Pronunciation,,0,0,0,,Ｗater Ball
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.18,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,水球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.69,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:14.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那棵树是我妈妈精心种植的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.82,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那可不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.87,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,神圣之力如芳醇之食粮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:26.37,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,赐予失去力量之人再次站起来的力量吧
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.37,Mushoku-Pronunciation,,0,0,0,,Healing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:27.37,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,哦  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你还会治愈魔法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,嗯  中级以下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,厉害  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.51,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,没什么  只要认真练习
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:42.64,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这种程度谁都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:44.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,看起来这家伙真容易攻略啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.14,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那么请做一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:47.93,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:53.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔法教科书里没有任何关于无咏唱的记载
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.86,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,虽然是在无意间使了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,其实是否触犯了什么禁忌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.11,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,洛琪希也说过需要咏唱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.66,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那么目前还是使用咏唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,说不定这很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,给予你所求之处以水之加护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:16.92,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:19.42,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你刚刚缩略咏唱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:24.55,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,平时都是缩略的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:30.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,平时都是无咏唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.35,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,无咏唱？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:33.69,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:35.90,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,平时都是无咏唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:37.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:41.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,看来很有培养价值呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:53.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,洛琪希小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:55.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,请不要把我们家的树当实验品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:57.00,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.97,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,一上来就犯错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,明天就是解雇了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.68,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,老师对不起  都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:10.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,伤脑筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:13.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,快二十年没和人说过话了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不知道这时应该说什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:18.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不  快想想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:20.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不是说过很多次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:23.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,色情游戏的主人公在这时会说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:29.12,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,老师刚刚没有失败
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是积累了经验
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:47.93,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.06,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,话说回来  洛琪希小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:52.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,进屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.98,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,先让我们互相介绍下自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:57.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:03.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,喂  快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.49,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但我没什么能作为回报的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:11.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好了  快进屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,鲁迪也快来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:18.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:28.18,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那么我们就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,小洛琪希的欢迎会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:33.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,仿佛在做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:36.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,被卡车撞上濒死的我在做的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:39.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不过就算是这样也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:41.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在这个世界的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:43.49,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我也应该可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:45.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,像人一样去生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:46.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,像人一样去努力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,遇上挫折也能再爬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.57,0:21:49.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,依旧继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:54.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就算是这样的我  也应该可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:57.54,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,没有工作  家里蹲  废物一般的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.00,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,也能够重新开始人生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:04.97,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,认真地活下去
